node.title: Homicide investigation underway after woman found dead in Christchurch home
node.description: A homicide investigation is underway after a 37-year-old woman was found dead in her Christchurch home yesterday evening.
node.content:
["A homicide investigation is underway after a woman was found dead in Christchurch.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Patrice Allen\n
", "The 37-year-old was found in her home in the suburb of Addington.", "Police said a scene examination of her Grove Road home is underway and part of the street is cordoned off."]
